      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MADE IN LONDON (1) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at The Gardens, but was among the placings at The Gardens three back. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. OCEAN'S PEARL (4) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.38 beating Koda Mulwee. Form from her last run is proving strong. Expecting another bold showing. TOMMIE'S BRIDE (3) boasts a consistent overall record including 13 wins from 49 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (17.94) over 300m at this track. Performs well off this draw. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. SHE'S SILKY (2) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.",
